      "content": "it just feels like there's no point to any of it. i wake up and the first thing i feel is this massive ache, and then i just spend the day waiting for it to be over. even when i try to do stuff, it's like i'm just going through the motions. i'm so exhausted from carrying this. i just want the ache to stop. i want everything to just be still.",
